manifest of src directory:

src/config.c
src/config.h: parse config file;

src/global_context.c
src/global_context.h: define global controlling variable;

src/image_capture.c
src/image_capture.h: capture image from v4l2, and convert to jpeg or h264;

src/image_convert.c
src/image_convert.h: convert image to RGB888 or YUV420P;

src/libx264.c
src/libx264.h: encode image (in YUV420P format) to h264 format;

src/log.c
src/log.h: log utils of the project;

src/path.c
src/path.h: filepath generation;

src/picture_thread.c
src/picture_thread.h: picture manipulation thread;

src/signal.c
src/signal.h: signal handling of the project;

src/v4l2_utils.c
src/v4l2_utils.h: linux v4l2 manipulation of the project;

src/video.c
src/video.h: video capture using linux v4l2;

src/video_thread.c
src/video_thread.h: video encode thread;


src/main.c: main entry of the project;
